{"id":29,"category_slug":"short-stories","category_name":"Short Stories","position":20,"title":"20. Working outside","subtitle":"","level":"A1","parts":25,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/short-stories/20-working-outside.29/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/20-working-outside-2019-03-20-08-39-58/0-20-working-outside.mp3","transcript":"Today I was working outside.\nIt was a sunny day,\nand I was very hot.\nI wore a hat on my head.\nI watered all the plants.\nI weeded the flower beds.\nI cut back all of the plants that were growing too big.\nI gave some of the plants plant food.\nI cut the lawn.\nI raked the lawn.\nI filled up the bird baths with water.\nI swept the sidewalks and the paths.\nI took out the garbage.\nI filled the car up with gas.\nI washed the car.\nI hung out the clothes on the clothesline.\nI washed down the lawn furniture.\nI washed all of the windows on the house from the outside.\nI was so tired.\nSo I had a glass of lemonade.\nI talked to my neighbor,\nand I helped her trim a tree.\nI planted some bulbs,\nand then I went into the house.\nI was exhausted.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:55:32","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Today I was working outside.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/20-working-outside-2019-03-20-08-39-58/1.mp3","time_start":1.8,"time_end":3.9},{"position":2,"content":"It was a sunny day,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/20-working-outside-2019-03-20-08-39-58/2.mp3","time_start":4.2,"time_end":5.52},{"position":3,"content":"and I was very hot.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/20-working-outside-2019-03-20-08-39-58/3.mp3","time_start":5.7,"time_end":7.07},{"position":4,"content":"I wore a hat on my head.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/20-working-outside-2019-03-20-08-39-58/4.mp3","time_start":7.4,"time_end":9.1},{"pos